'''Classic Adventure''', also known as ''Adventure 1'', is a fantasy text-based video game released by Abersoft in 1982. <ref>{{cite web|title=Classic Adventure|url=http://cpczone.emuunlim.org:88/reviews/index.php?title=408|website=CPC Zone|accessdate=24 August 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827115659/http://cpczone.emuunlim.org:88/reviews/index.php?title=408|archive-date=27 August 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref> It was originally released as ''Adventure 1'' on the ZX Spectrum in 1982 before being changed to ''Classic Adventure'' in 1984-1985 and re-released on more platforms.{{cn|date=August 2016}}

Classic Adventure is a remake of the 1976 text adventure game ''[[Colossal Cave Adventure]]''.{{cn|date=August 2016}}

==Gameplay==
As a text based game it starts with the opening "You are standing at the end of a road before a small brick building. Around you is a forest. A small stream flows out of the building and down a gully". From here it is up to the player to decide how to explore the caves in the game. There are obstacles that must be overcome and treasure to bring back to the house.{{cn|date=August 2016}}

